~   Given: f$_{r}$ = 159.155 Hz, L = 100mH, R = 1
~          X$_{L}$ = 2$\pi$fL = 2$\pi$(159.155)(100mH)=j100$\Omega$
~          X$_{C}$ = 1/(2$\pi$fC) = 1/(2$\pi$(159.155)(10$\mu$F)) = -j100$\Omega$
