\includegraphics{02500.eps} 
\caption{\sl TDX subtraction. } 
\label{02500.eps} 
\end{figure}

 

The torque inputs in Figure~\ref{02500.eps}  are TX and TDX. The torque output angular difference is TR.
 

 
\begin{figure}[hbtp!] 
\centering 
\includegraphics{02501.eps} 
\caption{\sl TDX Addition. } 
\label{02501.eps} 
\end{figure}

 

The torque inputs in Figure~\ref{02501.eps}   are TX and TDX. The torque output angular sum is TR.
 

 
\begin{figure}[hbtp!] 
\centering 
\includegraphics{02502.eps} 
\caption{\sl TDR subtraction. } 
\label{02502.eps} 
\end{figure}

 

The torque inputs in Figure~\ref{02502.eps} are TX$_{1}$ and TX$_{2}$. The torque output angular difference is TDR.
 

 
\begin{figure}[hbtp!] 
